sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Broker as Kafka Broker
    participant Deser as KafkaAvroDeserializer
    participant Cache as Local Schema Cache
    participant SR as Schema Registry
    participant App as Consumer App

    Broker->>Deser: Consume raw binary record value
    Deser->>Deser: Read 1st byte (confirm Magic Byte = 0x00)
    
    alt Magic Byte is Missing
        Deser-->>App: Throw SerializationException ('Unknown Magic Byte')
    else Magic Byte Valid
        Deser->>Deser: Read next 4 bytes (extract Schema ID, e.g., ID 42)
        Deser->>Cache: Query cache for Schema ID 42
        
        alt Schema ID 42 in Cache
            Cache-->>Deser: Return parsed Avro schema
        else Schema ID 42 NOT in Cache
            Deser->>SR: GET /schemas/ids/42
            SR-->>Deser: Return raw Avro schema JSON
            Deser->>Deser: Parse and compile Avro schema
            Deser->>Cache: Cache Schema ID 42 with compiled schema
        end
        
        Deser->>Deser: Deserialize remaining bytes using Avro schema
        Deser-->>App: Return deserialized Java Object / Python Dict
    end
